Janice GLANZ, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
ONEWEST BANK, N.A. n/k/a CIT Bank, N.A., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D16-3280 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. March 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Pursuant to the notice of voluntary dismissal filed herein, this appeal is dismissed.

The appellee's motion for extension of time is denied as moot.
